---
title: One-Pot Moroccan Lamb Meatball & Veggie Stew with Couscous, Extra Yoghurt & Mint
description: How can you possibly improve on lamb meatballs stewed in a perfectly spiced tomato-based sauce with all your favourite veg?
Cook it all in one pot! Served upon a bed of fluffy couscous with cooling yoghurt and fragrant mint on top, this dish goes straight
to the top of the charts.
